<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hora - Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden;">
        
        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; color: white;">
            <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Hora</div>
            <div style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; font-weight: 300;">Time Tracking Made Simple</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div style="padding: 40px 30px;">
            <h1 style="color: #2d3748; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.3;">üîë Reset Your Password</h1>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Hi <strong>{{user_name}}</strong>,
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                We received a request to reset the password for your Hora account. Click the button below to create a new password:
            </p>
            
            <!-- Reset Button -->
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{reset_link}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">
                    Reset Password
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                This password reset link will expire in <strong>1 hour</strong> for security reasons.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Security Tips -->
            <div style="background-color: #fef5e7; border-left: 4px solid #f6ad55; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
                <p style="color: #975a16; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">üõ°Ô∏è Security Tips:</p>
                <p style="color: #975a16; margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px;">‚Ä¢ Use a strong password with at least 8 characters</p>
                <p style="color: #975a16; margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px;">‚Ä¢ Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</p>
                <p style="color: #975a16; margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px;">‚Ä¢ Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@hora.com" style="color: #667eea;">support@hora.com</a>
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The Hora Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="background-color: #2d3748; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">Hora</div>
            <p style="color: #a0aec0; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Making time tracking simple and efficient for teams worldwide.
            </p>
            
            <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <a href="{{app_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="{{help_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Help Center</a>
                <a href="{{contact_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Contact Us</a>
                <a href="{{privacy_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
                ¬© 2024 Hora. All rights reserved.<br>
                {{company_address}}
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 12px;">
                You're receiving this email because you have an account with Hora.<br>
                <a href="{{unsubscribe_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0;">Unsubscribe</a> from these notifications.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>